0.3.0.0

 - Drop support for GHC <=7.8
 - Add official support for GHC 8.0, 8.2 and 8.4
 - Remove `showData` API. As a replacement you can use GHC's HsDumpAst instead.

0.2.3.3

 - Fix incorrect CPP conditionals for GHC 8.0 (by @DanielG)

0.2.3.2

 - Fix packaging of test suite

0.2.3.1

 - Fix build for 8.2.1 (by @achirkin)
 - GHC 8.0+ is technically no longer supported (test suite fails)

0.2.2

 - Add staged variants for SYB combinators `somewhere`,
   `everythingBut`, `something`, `everywhereM`.
 - Avoid error thunks introduced in GHC 7.8.*
